  "img": "icons/environment/settlement/watchtower-city.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl72_LabelType\">You were part of a group that was mercilessly attacked by giants of the tundra, who may have gone so far as to eat the dead and dying. After that, little can faze you, but you strongly prefer to finish fights with giants quickly to prevent anything like that from happening again.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTraits_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl72_LabelType\">Tundra - Cloud, Frost, River, Rune, Taiga</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl72_LabelType\">You gain a +2 trait bonus on attack rolls to confirm critical hits against giants and on saving throws against fear effects.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl72_LabelType\"><strong>Likely Regions</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl72_LabelType\">Brevoy, Irrisen, Lands of the Linnorm Kings, Mendev, Realm of the Mammoth Lords.</span></p>",
